snippet.title: Best VGM 2404 - Shadow of the Colossus - In Awe of the Power ~ Battle With the Colossus
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 422 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7lHAHFl_3u0

Best VGM 1250 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lhVk4Q47cgQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS2 / PS3
Shadow of the Colossus (2005)
In Awe of the Power ~ Battle With the Colossus
Koh Otani
